    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A soft variety of copal resin obtained from species Agathis dammara native to the Philippines and Indonesia. It is used for varnishes and resin/oil media, and in many fixative recipes.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
